            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Hd1e108">Rubrica 10</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De misericordia et immisericordia</head>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e114">
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>¶ De misericordia et immisericordia. Rubrica 10
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e119">
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e116">IN exodo. capitulo 22.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e123">
               Adue<lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>nam non contri
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>stabis: neque affliges eum. Uidue et
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>pupillo non nocebis. Si leseritis eos
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>vociferabuntur ad me: et ego audiam clamorem
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>eorum. et idignabitur furor meus: percutiamque vos
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>gladio. et erunt vxores vestre vidue et filii 
               ve<lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>stri pupilli.</quote> 
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e142"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e139">22. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e144">Pauperis misereberis in 
               ne<lb ed="#V" n="22" break="no"/>gocio. Non declinabis in iudicio pauperis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>Peregrino molestus non eris.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e153">
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e154">In leuitico. capitulo 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e157">Non morabitur opus 
               mer<lb ed="#V" n="25" break="no"/>cenarii tui apud te vsque mane. Non 
               maledi<lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>ces surdo: nec coram ceco pones offendiculum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>Si habitauit aduena in terra vestra et moratus
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>fuerit inter vos: ne exprobretis ei: sed sit inter
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>vos quisi idigena.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e171"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e172">24. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e173">Equum iudicium sit inter
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>vos: siue pegrinus: siue ciuis peccauerit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e179">
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e184">Moyses in deuteronomio. capitulo 27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e183">Maledictus
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>qui errare facit cecum in itinere. Maledictus qui 
               per<lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>uertit iudicium aduene et pupilli et vidue.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e191">
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e198"><sic>Thobie</sic> <sic>hystoria</sic>. capitulo 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e195">Noli auertere faciem tuam
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>ab vllo paupere. ita enim fiet vt nec a te 
               auerte<lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>rur facies domini. Quicumque tibi aliquid operatus
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>fuerit statim ei mercedem restitue. et merces 
               mer<lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>cenarii tui apud te omnino non remaneat.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e207">
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e216">Psalmista. 9. psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e211">Patientia pauperum non 
               peri<lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>bit in finem.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e217"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e226">40. psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e219">Beatus qui intelligit super 
               ege<lb ed="#V" n="41" break="no"/>num: et pauperem in die mala liberabit eum dominus.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e226">
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e239">160. psalmus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e230">Faciet iudicium dominus inopis: et 
               vin<lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>dictam pauperum.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e236"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e249">166. psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e238">Dominus custodit 
               ad<lb ed="#V" n="44" break="no"/>uenas: pupillum et viduam suscipiet.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e244">
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e261">Salomon in prouerbiis. capitulo 14.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e248">Etiam proximo suo <!--322.xml-->
          <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>pauper odiosus erit. Qui miseretur pauperi beatus
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>erit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e260"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e277">17. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e262">Qui despicit pauperem exprobrat
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>factori eius. Qui in ruina letatur alterius: non erit
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>inpunitus.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e270"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e289">18. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e272">Cum obsecrationibus loquitur
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>pauper.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e278"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e299">19. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e280">Fres hominis pauperis oderut eum:
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>insuper et amici procul recesserunt ab eo. Feneratur
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>domino qui miseretur pauperis et vicissitudinem suam 
               re<lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>det ei.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e291"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e314">21. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e293">Qui obturat aurem suam ad 
               cla<lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>morem pauperis: et ipse clamabit et non exaudietur</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e299">
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e326">22. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e303">Non facies violentiam pauperi: quia pauper est
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>neque conteres egenum in porta: quia dominus 
               iu<lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>dicabit causam eius.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e311">
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e340">Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiastico. capitulo 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e315">Oculos 
               tu<lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>os transferas a paupere. Non exasperes pauperem in
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>inopia sua. Cor inopis ne afflixeris: et non 
               protra<lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>has datum angustianti. Rogationem contribulanti
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>nec abiicias: et ne auertas faciem tuam ab 
               ege<lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>no. In iudicando esto pupillis misericors vt
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>pater: et pro viro matri illorum.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-d1e332"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Rd1e361">13. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08576-Qd1e334">Pascua 
               diui<lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>tum sunt pauperes. Humilis cum ceciderit expelletur et
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>a notis. Humilis deceptus est: insuper et arguitur: 
               lo<lb ed="#V" n="67" break="no"/>cutus est sensate: et no est ei datus locus.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
